theorem Topology.interior_has_P3 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    Topology.P3 (A := interior A) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P3]
  intro x hx
  have h_subset : interior A ⊆ interior (closure (interior A)) := by
    have h_closure : interior A ⊆ closure (interior A) := subset_closure
    exact interior_mono h_closure
  exact h_subset hx

import Mathlib
import Aesop

namespace Topology

variable {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]

def P1 (A : Set X) : Prop :=
  A ⊆ closure (interior A)

def P2 (A : Set X) : Prop :=
  A ⊆ interior (closure (interior A))

def P3 (A : Set X) : Prop :=
  A ⊆ interior (closure A)

theorem P2_implies_P3 {A : Set X} (h : P2 A) : P3 A := by
  dsimp [P2, P3] at *
  intro x hxA
  have hxInt : x ∈ interior (closure (interior A)) := h hxA
  have h_closure_subset : closure (interior A) ⊆ closure A :=
    closure_mono interior_subset
  have h_int_subset : interior (closure (interior A)) ⊆ interior (closure A) :=
    interior_mono h_closure_subset
  exact h_int_subset hxInt

theorem P2_implies_P1 {A : Set X} (h : P2 A) : P1 A := by
  dsimp [P2, P1] at *
  exact subset_trans h interior_subset

theorem P2_implies_P1_and_P3 {A : Set X} (h : P2 A) : P1 A ∧ P3 A := by
  exact ⟨P2_implies_P1 h, P2_implies_P3 h⟩

/-- If `A ⊆ interior (closure (interior A))`, then `closure A = closure (interior A)`. -/
theorem closure_eq_of_P2 {A : Set X} (h : P2 A) :
    closure A = closure (interior A) := by
  apply le_antisymm
  · -- `closure A ⊆ closure (interior A)`
    have hsub : A ⊆ closure (interior A) := (P2_implies_P1 (A := A) h)
    exact closure_minimal hsub isClosed_closure
  · -- `closure (interior A) ⊆ closure A`
    exact closure_mono interior_subset

end Topology

theorem Topology.P2_iff_P3_of_isOpen {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA : IsOpen A) : Topology.P2 (A := A) ↔ Topology.P3 A := by
  dsimp [Topology.P2, Topology.P3]
  simpa [hA.interior_eq]
